                            טיפים מתקדמים
===============================================================================

### 🚀 אופטימיזציה:

#### שיפור ביצועים:
```
Add these performance optimizations:
"Implement lazy loading for images and charts
Use virtual scrolling for large lists
Compress API responses
Use CDN for static assets
Enable browser caching"
```

#### שיפור UX:
```
Add these UX improvements:
"Show loading states for all actions
Add smooth transitions between pages
Implement undo/redo functionality
Add keyboard shortcuts for common actions
Show progress indicators for long operations"
```

#### שיפור אבטחה:
```
Add these security features:
"Validate all user inputs
Sanitize HTML content
Use HTTPS for all communications
Implement rate limiting
Add CSRF protection"
```

### 🎨 עיצוב מתקדם:

#### נושא כהה:
```
Add dark theme support:
"Implement dark/light theme toggle
Use Hebrew labels for theme options
Maintain RTL layout in both themes
Ensure proper contrast for Hebrew text
Save theme preference in localStorage"
```

#### עיצוב מותאם:
```
Add customization options:
"Allow users to customize colors
Add different font size presets
Implement layout density options
Add custom dashboard arrangements
Allow hiding/showing interface elements"
```

